                <![CDATA[<b>Parts Advisor:</b> <i>“Sorry about that. Where were we? Oh yes, you were asking about parts for front brakes on a Jeep Patriot and I asked if you have the VIN for the vehicle.”</i>]]>
</bodyBullet>
              <bodyBullet id="bb2" order="22">
                <![CDATA[<b>Customer:</b> <i>“Yes, I do. It’s 1J8FT28088D679188.”</i>]]>
</bodyBullet>
              <bodyBullet id="bb3" order="24">
                <![CDATA[<b>Parts Advisor:</b> <i>"Thank you. I see that’s a 2008 model year Patriot. Do you know the distance traveled on the vehicle?”</i>]]>
</bodyBullet>
              <bodyBullet id="bb4" order="26">
