              <bodyBullet id="bb1" order="20" yPad="0">
                <![CDATA[<b>Parts Advisor:</b> <i>“So, you’re going to be doing some work on your Patriot’s front brakes. We’ve found the brake pads and calipers that you need for that in our parts catalog. Did you know that you’ll also need washers to seal the brake hose to the caliper? These are Mopar original equipment parts, so they’re engineered specifically for your vehicle.”</i>]]>
