                <![CDATA[<b>Parts Advisor:</b> <i>“Hi, this is Pete in Parts at Hometown Chrysler Dodge Jeep Ram calling back. I’ve found the parts you need for your brake repair. I can have them for you by 4:00 this afternoon. Would you like to pick them up then?”</i>]]>
