</bodyBullet>
              <bodyBullet id="bb3" order="21" time="1">
                <![CDATA[<b>Parts Advisor:</b> <i>“So, I’m hearing that you’re not sure you’re getting a good value for your money. Is that right?”</i>]]>
</bodyBullet>
              <bodyBullet id="bb4" order="26" time="1">
